# Claude Code subagent worktrees — git worktrees the Agent tool spins up
# under `isolation: "worktree"`. Real working trees with their own checkouts;
# they shouldn't pollute git status here OR trip biome's config discovery
# (their full biome.json copy makes biome see two competing root configs).
.claude/worktrees/
